A scenery that makes you swoon via @terplanet. In this coastal corner of Puglia, this incredibly romantic hideaway makes the perfect setup for special occasions and celebratory meals. 🍷

Known as one of Italy's most famous regions, Puglia features ancient towns, fine architecture, and divine cuisine that any culture aficionado will love. This sun-soaked landscape is best-visited from May to October when the weather is most pleasant. ✨

Is Puglia at the top of your Italy bucket list? What regions in Italy are your favorite and why? 🇮🇹

Absolutely breathtaking
📍Diamond Beach, Nusa Penida Island!💎 Have you ever been to Indonesia?😍

📌”Nusa Penida is an island southeast of Indonesia's island Bali and a district of Klungkung Regency that includes the neighbouring small island of Nusa Lembongan and twelve even smaller islands. The Badung Strait separates the island and Bali. The interior of Nusa Penida is hilly with a maximum altitude of 524 metres.” 
🎥 @naturebeauty8967
Via @earthbestshots
